    <div class="md-interesting-facts-box fact-box-details md-striped md-content-module-right">
        <div class="fact-box">
            <!DOCTYPE HTML><dl data-label="did you know?"><dt class="fact-list">did you know?</dt><dd><ul class="imars-list-itemized"><li>The longest recorded sieges of the era lasted several months.<br></li> <li>400 years afterwards, when Homer would have been writing, the ruins of Troy would have still been observable.<br></li> <li>Troy is a UNESCO World Heritage site.<br></li></ul></dd></dl></div>
    </div>

